  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a mixing bowl, combine poppy seeds with almond flour, coconut oil, and vanilla extract.",
    "Stir in agave nectar or maple syrup until well combined. Add ground flaxseed, cacao powder, and pinch of salt; mix thoroughly.",
    "Pour mixture into a lined baking dish and bake for 25-30 minutes or until golden brown on top.",
    "Let cool before serving."
